1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:03,220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 26]

5
00:01:14,270 --> 00:01:16,420
On this mission, we must seize the Divine Tree's power

6
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,340
and restore Dizang Sect's glory!

7
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,030
[The Divine Tree emerges]

8
00:01:22,030 --> 00:01:23,420
Why does the Wuyue Court mobilize all forces

9
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,780
to put Lifei on public trial

10
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,140
before the Mountain and Sea Sects?

11
00:01:31,390 --> 00:01:31,890
Master,

12
00:01:32,550 --> 00:01:34,010
could they kill Lifei to grab

13
00:01:34,670 --> 00:01:35,940
the Divine Tree's power?

14
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:38,010
From despair comes rebirth.

15
00:01:38,390 --> 00:01:40,220
There is surely sound sense

16
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,730
in Mr. Zuo Qiu's arrangements.

17
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,530
Let us wait and watch.

18
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,370
Your Highness, what should we do now?

19
00:01:51,370 --> 00:01:52,080
[The Divine Tree emerges]

20
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,140
Shall we gather men to rescue Lifei now?

21
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,450
Did the Chufeng Academy

22
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:02,290
leak this news?

23
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:03,860
Yes.

24
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,940
Heaven watches over us and protects our clan.

25
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:42,060
I firmly believe Your Lordship will gain a new life.

26
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:43,690
For five centuries,

27
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,220
I snuck into the Wuyue Court countless times,

28
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,690
only to search for Qingcheng and Your Lordship.

29
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:49,740
Guangwei wounded me

30
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,340
on my last try.

31
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,250
Luckily, when his beloved disciple

32
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:55,690
Yue Cailing chased me,

33
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:56,650
I seized her mortal vessel.

34
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:59,220
While recovering in Lugong Town,

35
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:01,340
I finally awaited your return.

36
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,650
This is great, my Lord.

37
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,410
So,

38
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:09,250
in the cave outside Lugong Town back then,

39
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,460
you already knew who I was.

40
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,850
You summoned the bone-devouring butterfly

41
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:17,220
and made Songfeng fall into darkness, too.

42
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:20,810
Lei Xiuyuan,

43
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,220
how come you're conscious?

44
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,940
You were poisoned by Soul-Bewitching Vines.

45
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,130
Mere Soul-Bewitching Vines

46
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,130
can never control me.

47
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,970
I never intended to control you.

48
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:43,370
I only hoped you'd remember you're Yecha.

49
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:44,130
All I've ever been

50
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,340
is Lei Xiuyuan.

51
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:47,780
I don't understand.

52
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,090
What joy is there in living as a human?

53
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:51,940
Do you still dream of staying forever with the Divine Tree?

54
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,060
I'm nothing like you.

55
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:56,460
All I want is to live as a human,

56
00:03:57,760 --> 00:04:00,220
an ordinary man in this world.

57
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:03,940
I made a promise to Lu,

58
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:05,810
yet I broke it.

59
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:07,900
This time,

60
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:09,780
I'll not go back on my word.

61
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,250
You!

62
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,340
Rakshasa,

63
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,780
you've caused trouble time and again.

64
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,570
I cannot spare you any longer.

65
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:26,010
Spare me, My Lord!

66
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,420
Show mercy!

67
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,540
Cuixuan

68
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:34,330
has captured Jiang Lifei.

69
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,980
They will destroy the Divine Tree.

70
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:40,100
Just like a thousand years ago,

71
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:44,450
they will tear her apart and feed on her power

72
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,450
until her soul vanishes completely.

73
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:57,620
My Lord!

74
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,740
You claim to be the top cultivator of the immortal sects.

75
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:32,330
Why do you need my master's Senluo Grand Art?

76
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:37,370
I see.

77
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,940
Without the miniature realm

78
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,740
and the wronged demon spirit,

79
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:46,210
you can never cultivate and ascend.

80
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,980
Stop daydreaming.

81
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,740
I'd rather die than give it to you.

82
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,330
We'll see

83
00:05:58,470 --> 00:06:00,450
how tough you are.

84
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:17,860
You imprisoned my master

85
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:21,370
all for your greedy ambition.

86
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:22,180
Silence!

87
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,330
Everything I've done

88
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:28,060
is for the immortal sects' grand cause.

89
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,300
Absorbing demon spirits

90
00:06:32,350 --> 00:06:33,540
and slaying fellow cultivators

91
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,100
are what you call the grand cause?

92
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:40,860
If they saw you kill my master

93
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:43,690
and piles of bones in the miniature realm,

94
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:46,500
would they still buy your lies?

95
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,660
The miniature realm has been destroyed.

96
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:51,300
No one will believe a word

97
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,130
of what you say.

98
00:06:53,910 --> 00:06:54,620
True,

99
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,500
I have no proof.

100
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,570
But my master once said

101
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,690
justice prevails in this world.

102
00:07:04,710 --> 00:07:05,860
What justice?

103
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,250
What even is justice?

104
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,250
With the Fruit of the Divine Tree,

105
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:12,180
I'll have endless spirit energy.

106
00:07:12,710 --> 00:07:14,420
Once my cultivation reaches perfection

107
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,860
and I become an immortal,

108
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:20,180
every word and deed of mine shall be the rules

109
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,300
and the heavenly law itself.

110
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,370
Your master is far too naive

111
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:29,620
to still believe in karmic retribution.

112
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,890
You have no right to mention him!

113
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,540
Stop struggling.

114
00:07:44,470 --> 00:07:47,130
Even your master could not break these spirit-sealing chains,

115
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:49,810
let alone you.

116
00:07:52,230 --> 00:07:53,180
Master.

117
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:57,330
Don't move!

118
00:08:07,150 --> 00:08:09,660
You tricked my master back by using your bond

119
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,660
as fellow disciples,

120
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,500
locked him in the miniature realm, and tortured him.

121
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,300
He was your senior brother.

122
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,540
Do you have any conscience left?

123
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,300
He wronged me first.

124
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,890
Years ago, Yecha left me gravely wounded.

125
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,660
As my fellow disciple,

126
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:31,010
he refused to heal me with the Divine Tree and demon spirits,

127
00:08:31,790 --> 00:08:33,540
was obsessed with building the Outcast Tomb,

128
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:35,730
and sealed all demon spirits away.

129
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,940
Where

130
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,780
was our bond back then?

131
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:44,450
He was stopping you from falling into darkness.

132
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,060
He fell into darkness!

133
00:08:46,350 --> 00:08:47,780
His heart belonged to foreign lands,

134
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,540
and he betrayed our sect,

135
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:55,730
leaving us his junior disciples to fend for ourselves.

136
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,060
I trusted him with all my heart once,

137
00:08:59,710 --> 00:09:00,420
yet

138
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,780
look what he did.

139
00:09:03,830 --> 00:09:05,300
He betrayed the sect.

140
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:09,060
I hate how he cannot tell right from wrong.

141
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,610
He never repented even till his last breath.

142
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,690
Narrow-minded wretches

143
00:09:14,710 --> 00:09:16,970
will never understand embracing all beings,

144
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:18,060
nor compassion for every living soul.

145
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:20,210
All you see

146
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:23,060
is the fake miniature realm.

147
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,690
You are filled with hatred,

148
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:27,450
dwelling in suspicion and wariness all the time,

149
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,850
yet you dream of controlling heavenly law.

150
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,490
Ridiculous.

151
00:09:35,470 --> 00:09:36,300
So what?

152
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:39,660
No matter how well Qingcheng hid you,

153
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:43,450
you shall end up in my hands.

154
00:09:53,990 --> 00:09:56,210
I'll refine you into a vessel

155
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:57,420
and absorb all your spirit energy

156
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:00,210
to become the supreme cultivator.

157
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:03,330
Then I will unify all immortal sects,

158
00:10:03,350 --> 00:10:04,450
wipe out the demon clan,

159
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,900
and rewrite the world's rules.

160
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:08,420
As the saying goes,

161
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,260
those who obey me shall thrive;

162
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,780
those who oppose me shall perish.

163
00:10:35,230 --> 00:10:35,850
Cuixuan,

164
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:38,690
dozens of immortal sects are breaking the barrier,

165
00:10:38,990 --> 00:10:40,020
claiming they wish to see the Divine Tree.

166
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,940
How did they learn that?

167
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,020
What one does,

168
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:50,140
heaven witnesses.

169
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,060
Do you think you can hide everything

170
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,380
and control all under heaven?

171
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:25,300
Elder Cuixuan,

172
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,540
since the Divine Tree is in your possession,

173
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,540
why keep it concealed?

174
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:31,690
What do you plan to do with it next?

175
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:40,300
Matters of the Wuyue Court

176
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,570
hardly require any explanation to you.

177
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,420
That's not how it works.

178
00:11:47,470 --> 00:11:48,780
The demon clan has run rampant lately.

179
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:51,300
Many immortal cultivators have fallen victim.

180
00:11:51,990 --> 00:11:54,020
The Sea Calamity is also drawing near.

181
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:55,610
The Divine Tree concerns the safety

182
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,060
of every sect

183
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,180
and the Central Plains.

184
00:11:58,470 --> 00:11:59,140
How can you claim

185
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,780
it's only Wuyue Court's business?

186
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,210
Am I right, everyone?

187
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:03,900
- Yes. - Exactly!

188
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:04,490
Yeah.

189
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:05,940
In the wars against demons years ago,

190
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:09,180
Dizang Sect's ancestors were wounded by the Divine Tree.

191
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:11,300
It owes our sect a blood debt

192
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:12,850
that cannot be ignored.

193
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:14,210
True!

194
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,090
The Divine Tree also harmed our ancestors.

195
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,060
Right!

196
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,970
We must stand united

197
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,850
against this outsider.

198
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:21,900
Indeed.

199
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,540
We ought to deal with it together

200
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:24,540
and discuss a solution side by side.

201
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,180
Let's discuss a solution.

202
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,140
Everyone, listen!

203
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:33,690
You've all traveled far today.

204
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,780
You may rest first.

205
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:38,060
Word spreads that the Divine Tree colludes with the demon clan.

206
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,850
Every day we delay

207
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,690
brings greater peril.

208
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,060
We must resolve this without delay.

209
00:12:46,710 --> 00:12:47,850
I share

210
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:50,970
your worries.

211
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,730
That is why I sealed all news

212
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:56,850
and imprisoned the Divine Tree.

213
00:12:58,990 --> 00:12:59,610
Yet

214
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,140
since you have gathered here,

215
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:04,610
tomorrow, I shall hold a public trial

216
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,940
of the Divine Tree with all of you.

217
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:10,180
What do you say?

218
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,020
Zhaomin.

219
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:38,450
Elder Cuixuan has laid secret restriction spells

220
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,660
all around the Wuyue Shrine.

221
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,540
Do not force your way in.

222
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,180
Later, Zhaomin and I

223
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,540
will draw off the guards outside.

224
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:49,780
Use this to slice open

225
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,020
the barrier temporarily.

226
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,300
But Elder Cuixuan will sense it for sure,

227
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:54,610
so you must move fast.

228
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,810
If you fail to rescue Lifei in time,

229
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,730
retreat at once.

230
00:13:59,160 --> 00:13:59,940
We'll rethink our plan.

231
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:02,850
Deng and I cannot openly defy our sect.

232
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,970
We appreciate you risking your lives.

233
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,210
Thank you both on behalf of Lifei.

234
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:08,850
No need for formalities.

235
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:10,330
Lifei is family to me.

236
00:14:10,350 --> 00:14:11,380
I'll save her no matter what.

237
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:14,020
This is nothing like what happened in Duanming City.

238
00:14:14,350 --> 00:14:15,730
If Elder Cuixuan catches us,

239
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:16,900
we'll be branded traitors

240
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,300
colluding with outsiders,

241
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,940
and we might even lose our lives.

242
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:21,900
Last time in Duanming City,

243
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:23,610
Lifei risked her life for the Jiufeng Clan.

244
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:25,940
My clan always repays kindness.

245
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:28,900
What about the Wanxian Sect?

246
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,450
The Sea Sects have always been seen

247
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:32,490
as outsiders by the Mountain Sects.

248
00:14:32,830 --> 00:14:34,330
My master approved our trip here.

249
00:14:34,830 --> 00:14:35,690
I don't mind getting dragged

250
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:36,210
into trouble.

251
00:15:03,710 --> 00:15:07,540
Cuixuan must be troubled by those immortal sects.

252
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:10,780
So,

253
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:14,210
have you agreed on how to split my power?

254
00:15:16,470 --> 00:15:17,450
We'll decide what to do with you

255
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:18,570
after the public trial tomorrow

256
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:20,060
at Chen hour.

257
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,090
I once

258
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:27,180
asked you to be my cultivation partner

259
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,780
and practice with me,

260
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:30,850
yet you refused time and again.

261
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:33,490
Never thought

262
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:36,490
you'd end up like this today.

263
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,940
I thought you still held old affection

264
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:42,810
and came to see me.

265
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:45,690
Turns out you're just here to gloat.

266
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,730
I do have a lingering fondness for you.

267
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,540
If you change your mind,

268
00:15:56,590 --> 00:15:58,450
I might take you away.

269
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,570
Can you undo

270
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,020
these chains on me?

271
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,730
Seems we were never fated to be together.

272
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:15,730
Since things cannot go as we wish,

273
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:17,810
why not

274
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,330
share some

275
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:21,450
of your spirit energy with me?

276
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:26,810
You also want my spirit energy?

277
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:30,610
You're doomed anyway.

278
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:33,450
Leave a trace of your energy for me.

279
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:38,380
Very well.

280
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:42,850
Better to give it to you

281
00:16:44,590 --> 00:16:45,610
than let that old villain Cuixuan seize it.

282
00:16:47,230 --> 00:16:48,780
You treated me kindly once, after all.

283
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:52,300
Rest assured.

284
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:54,090
I'll be gentle,

285
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,570
and you won't suffer any pain.

286
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,820
You worry too much.

287
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,450
I'm bound by spirit-sealing chains,

288
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:12,580
unable to move an inch.

289
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:14,820
No need to be so cautious.

290
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,050
You planned to use spirit absorption against me.

291
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,490
Cunning as ever, Lifei.

292
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,490
Death draws near,

293
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:27,210
yet you still scheme against me.

294
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,340
Then do not blame me

295
00:17:29,990 --> 00:17:31,490
for showing no mercy.

296
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:57,690
What's this?

297
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,380
You want the Divine Tree's power, right?

298
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:02,900
Take it.

299
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,010
Lifei!

300
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:17,860
What brings you here?

301
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,210
It won't work.

302
00:18:22,790 --> 00:18:23,450
Let me try again.

303
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:24,380
There has to be a way.

304
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:33,290
Even the Wuyue Court's treasures

305
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:35,940
cannot break these chains.

306
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:39,050
Better spare the effort.

307
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:43,180
Useless fools!

308
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,340
Out of respect for Mr. Shen,

309
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,250
I shall spare your lives for now.

310
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,660
You may stay and accompany her

311
00:18:50,120 --> 00:18:51,690
through her final moments.

312
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:13,380
I've dragged you into trouble.

313
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:15,580
Truth is, I'm...

314
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:16,290
The Divine Tree.

315
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:18,100
We already know.

316
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,380
We suspected it back in Duantu.

317
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:26,140
Tongzhou and Xiuyuan must have known, too.

318
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,100
That's why they sent Miaoqing to stand in for you.

319
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:32,970
So many have suffered because of me.

320
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,340
Gelin,

321
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,770
as you knew my identity all along,

322
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:39,730
you never should have come.

323
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:41,340
Don't talk nonsense.

324
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:42,690
We knew each other young

325
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:43,380
and walked through things together.

326
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:44,660
Because you're the Divine Tree,

327
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:45,860
you cease to be one of us?

328
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:47,620
What?

329
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,530
The Divine Tree looks down on us?

330
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:51,050
Think we're not worthy to be your friends?

331
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:55,010
We'll always be friends.

332
00:19:59,120 --> 00:19:59,860
I just...

333
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:00,620
Don't worry.

334
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:02,900
Chongyi and Zhaomin are working on a plan.

335
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,660
We will get you out for sure.

336
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:07,490
Where's Xiuyuan?

337
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,100
I heard the demon clan took him hostage.

338
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:11,620
Is his life in danger?

339
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:20,770
He

340
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,900
should be fine.

341
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,820
With his cultivation and wits,

342
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:27,450
he'll turn misfortune into safety.

343
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,660
But what about you?

344
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,290
Tomorrow's public trial

345
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,380
will have every sect watching.

346
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,690
No one knows

347
00:20:32,710 --> 00:20:33,380
what they'll do to you.

348
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,420
I've been waiting for this trial.

349
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:12,180
Disguising herself as the Chufeng Academy's disciple,

350
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,860
the Divine Tree infiltrated the Wuyue Court

351
00:21:13,990 --> 00:21:15,100
with malicious schemes.

352
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:18,530
I've found and captured her alive

353
00:21:19,230 --> 00:21:20,690
for this public trial.

354
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:38,770
Fellow cultivators,

355
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,660
do you have any questions?

356
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,210
Immortal Cuixuan,

357
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:59,730
I believe none of us will raise objections.

358
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,380
Everyone,

359
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:09,420
Lei Xiuyuan is a demon spy,

360
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,250
and Jiang Lifei is equally guilty.

361
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:14,140
In my opinion, no need for a trial.

362
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:17,100
The Divine Tree must not remain in the world.

363
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,050
Mr. Luo speaks the truth.

364
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:25,820
The previous Divine Tree helped the Demon Lord Yecha

365
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:29,010
slaughter countless cultivators.

366
00:22:29,510 --> 00:22:29,970
Today,

367
00:22:30,310 --> 00:22:31,820
we shall make her pay back

368
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:33,010
every last debt she owes us.

369
00:22:34,710 --> 00:22:35,340
Exactly.

370
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,340
Blood for blood.

371
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,210
The Divine Tree draws boundless spirit energy

372
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,210
from heaven and earth.

373
00:22:44,230 --> 00:22:44,820
I say

374
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,340
we all absorb her energy together

375
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:48,530
to boost our cultivation,

376
00:22:48,840 --> 00:22:49,620
fend off the Sea Calamity,

377
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,210
and defeat the demon clan.

378
00:22:51,400 --> 00:23:00,210
Fend off the Sea Calamity! Defeat the demon clan!

379
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:01,730
Enough!

380
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,690
All of you!

381
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:47,530
Can you all not contain your greed?

382
00:23:49,360 --> 00:23:51,730
The crimes of the old Divine Tree are not hers to bear.

383
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,340
In White Cliff and Duanming City,

384
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:54,730
Lifei only saved lives.

385
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:57,210
She has never harmed a single innocent soul,

386
00:23:57,990 --> 00:23:58,820
and every one of you

387
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:01,490
knows this full well.

388
00:24:08,750 --> 00:24:09,420
What is this?

389
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:12,620
Just because she bears the Divine Tree's power,

390
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,860
you seek to plunder her spiritual energy

391
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:16,380
without distinguishing right from wrong?

392
00:24:17,510 --> 00:24:18,660
If that is your intent,

393
00:24:19,360 --> 00:24:20,290
let me ask you all.

394
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:23,290
How are you any different

395
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,340
from the demon clan?

396
00:24:27,120 --> 00:24:27,450
You...

397
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:37,940
The Sea Calamity shall ruin the world,

398
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,490
and the innocents will perish.

399
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,690
Capturing the Divine Tree

400
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:43,730
is heaven's blessing,

401
00:24:44,550 --> 00:24:47,900
a sign that this power is meant to serve us.

402
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:51,730
We must not cling to misplaced mercy

403
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:54,050
and waste the blessing.

404
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,580
Immortal Cuixuan speaks the truth.

405
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,530
We must follow heaven's will,

406
00:24:59,070 --> 00:24:59,860
slay the Divine Tree,

407
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,050
and absorb her spirit energy!

408
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:12,420
Slay the Divine Tree! Absorb her energy!

409
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:12,900
Ridiculous.

410
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,690
Absorb my energy?

411
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,860
You're all absurd.

412
00:25:19,270 --> 00:25:20,010
Insolent witch!

413
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:22,050
Your end draws near. What's so funny?

414
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:32,250
I laugh at your naivety.

415
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:34,580
Do you believe Cuixuan will share

416
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:35,970
my energy with all of you?

417
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:39,450
How blind can you be?

418
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:43,450
Witch,

419
00:25:44,070 --> 00:25:45,580
cease your deceitful words to sow discord!

420
00:25:45,990 --> 00:25:47,580
Immortal Cuixuan is noble and selfless,

421
00:25:47,710 --> 00:25:48,690
devoted to the greater good.

422
00:25:49,230 --> 00:25:50,490
Never try to sow discord.

423
00:25:52,710 --> 00:25:53,580
The greater good?

424
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,970
Do you see these chains binding me?

425
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:06,770
Jiang Lifei,

426
00:26:07,710 --> 00:26:09,140
these chains look extraordinary.

427
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:10,770
What is the story behind them?

428
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:12,970
Lady Longjing,

429
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,730
you once aided me

430
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:18,050
and have seen through many things.

431
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,250
I'll tell you the truth out of goodwill.

432
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:24,820
Cuixuan designed

433
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,900
these dragon-binding spirit-sealing chains solely to subdue

434
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,860
my master Qingcheng.

435
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,690
They have fused deep into my bones and blood.

436
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,820
If you absorb my spirit energy,

437
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:43,730
the sealing spell will transfer into your bodies.

438
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:45,010
Then each of you

439
00:26:46,990 --> 00:26:49,010
will become Cuixuan's puppets.

440
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:57,380
Devious witch!

441
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:59,010
You're misleading everyone.

442
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:02,100
Don't trust

443
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:02,940
a monster's lies.

444
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,050
We are fellow immortal cultivators.

445
00:27:05,600 --> 00:27:07,210
Why would I harm any of you?

446
00:27:08,030 --> 00:27:10,180
Because you want to stand supreme under heaven.

447
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:11,660
Driven by this ambition,

448
00:27:12,990 --> 00:27:15,180
you murdered your senior brother Qingcheng,

449
00:27:16,360 --> 00:27:17,860
consorted with demons,

450
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:20,660
and drained stray spirits from foreign lands.

451
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,900
There is no evil you would not commit.

452
00:27:28,600 --> 00:27:30,250
Now that you possess me,

453
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:32,380
you'd never share my energy with others.

454
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,380
Qingcheng is dead?

455
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,450
He perished

456
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,970
in Cuixuan's miniature realm.

457
00:27:53,470 --> 00:27:54,820
You may verify this

458
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,900
at his former residence on Hushe Peak.

459
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:58,940
Cuixuan,

460
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:01,250
was what she said the truth?

461
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:06,940
Guangwei,

462
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:09,420
do not believe her slander.

463
00:28:12,990 --> 00:28:13,580
Witch,

464
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:15,380
stop clouding our judgment.

465
00:28:15,790 --> 00:28:17,010
Do you think sowing discord among us

466
00:28:17,230 --> 00:28:18,420
will spare your life?

467
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,250
Zhaomin,

468
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,900
I'm thirsty.

469
00:28:54,310 --> 00:28:55,100
Watch out, it's a trap!

470
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:24,100
Qingcheng.

471
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:25,770
Qingcheng.

472
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:30,420
Qingcheng!

473
00:29:35,470 --> 00:29:37,450
If they saw you kill my master

474
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:40,340
and piles of bones in the miniature realm,

475
00:29:40,840 --> 00:29:42,490
would they still buy your lies?

476
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:45,290
The miniature realm has been destroyed.

477
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,580
No one will believe a word

478
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,140
of what you say.

479
00:29:56,920 --> 00:30:01,770
I've long heard that Qingcheng's Senluo Grand Art

480
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,420
can trace back to past events.

481
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:07,290
So she is really his disciple.

482
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:14,620
I'll refine you into a vessel

483
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,730
and absorb all your spirit energy

484
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:18,690
to become the supreme cultivator.

485
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:21,050
Then I will unify all immortal sects,

486
00:30:21,070 --> 00:30:22,140
wipe out the demon clan,

487
00:30:22,360 --> 00:30:24,660
and rewrite the world's rules.

488
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:25,530
As the saying goes,

489
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,050
those who obey me shall thrive;

490
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:29,940
those who oppose me shall perish.

491
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,660
Why?

492
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:39,050
Why did you kill Qingcheng?

493
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:42,820
You two used to be the closest friends.

494
00:30:45,070 --> 00:30:47,100
He colluded with monsters

495
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:48,660
and sheltered demons,

496
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,860
making him a traitor to all immortal sects.

497
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:52,940
I had every right

498
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:53,730
to slay him.

499
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,140
You killed him,

500
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:02,490
so I will avenge him!

501
00:31:03,270 --> 00:31:03,900
Chongyi.

502
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:04,900
- Let me go! - Cuixuan.

503
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:05,770
- Calm your rage. - Release me!

504
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,050
Let go of me!

505
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:07,770
Facing the Sea Calamity,

506
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:08,900
don't turn on one another.

507
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,250
We care nothing

508
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,010
for your sect's feuds

509
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:13,580
over Qingcheng.

510
00:31:14,070 --> 00:31:16,050
Today, we must absorb the Divine Tree's power.

511
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:16,660
Exactly.

512
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:19,940
The Divine Tree will only bring disasters.

513
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:20,860
I say

514
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,660
we consume her power together.

515
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:32,140
You think you can absorb the power?

516
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:42,690
All those peerless, extraordinary talents

517
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,580
perished centuries ago.

518
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:48,690
Only mediocre folk like you remain,

519
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:51,210
occupying positions yet accomplishing nothing.

520
00:31:52,440 --> 00:31:54,420
For you to absorb the power

521
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,770
is akin to burning lutes to cook cranes,

522
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:57,860
a waste of divine treasure.

523
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:00,900
Far better to channel all its power into me alone.

524
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:03,010
With my strength,

525
00:32:03,710 --> 00:32:05,210
I can withstand the Sea Calamity

526
00:32:05,510 --> 00:32:06,820
and wipe out the demon clan.

527
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,250
Have you lost your mind?

528
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:09,820
Cuixuan,

529
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,490
you're talking nonsense.

530
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:12,770
Guangwei,

531
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,690
you were gravely wounded by Yecha,

532
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:18,380
stunting your cultivation forever.

533
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:21,580
Don't you wish to wipe away this humiliation?

534
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:23,450
I stand irreconcilably against the demon clan.

535
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,290
Yet all you've done

536
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,690
is no different from them.

537
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:29,690
You are stubborn beyond reasoning.

538
00:32:29,710 --> 00:32:30,180
You...

539
00:32:31,710 --> 00:32:32,290
Cuixuan,

540
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:33,210
turn back

541
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,380
while there is still time.

542
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,620
What are you trying to do?

543
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:44,730
Move aside.

544
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,010
Move aside!

545
00:32:55,600 --> 00:32:56,900
The Divine Tree belongs to the Lantian Sect!

546
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,050
No, it belongs to the Dizang Sect!

547
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,620
- Seize it! - Hurry, move!

548
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,620
- Hurry. - Go after her!

549
00:33:02,840 --> 00:33:03,420
Protect Lifei!

550
00:33:04,470 --> 00:33:05,420
The Divine Tree is ours!

551
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,450
Stay back!

552
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,380
Guard Lifei at all costs!

553
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:12,210
Stay back!

554
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:14,380
The Divine Tree is ours.

555
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:15,770
She is ours!

556
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:17,210
Don't fight us for her.

557
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:19,660
No one can take her from us!

558
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:22,730
Move aside!

559
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:23,730
Step away!

560
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,450
Hand her over to us.

561
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:40,620
She's ours!

562
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,050
She is ours.

563
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,250
She belongs to our sect!

564
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,530
She's ours!

565
00:33:56,710 --> 00:33:57,530
Step aside!

566
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:00,820
Ours.

567
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:01,820
Master,

568
00:34:03,510 --> 00:34:05,820
are they the ones you swore to protect?

569
00:34:07,990 --> 00:34:09,860
- Move aside! - This treasure is ours!

570
00:34:11,240 --> 00:34:12,260
She's ours.

571
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:16,530
Lifei!

572
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,420
Lifei!

573
00:34:19,550 --> 00:34:20,610
The Divine Tree is ours.

574
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:21,900
She is ours.

575
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:27,820
- Give her to me! - Move aside!

576
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,940
The Divine Tree belongs to our sect!

577
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,220
Master,

578
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:36,610
I've done all I could.

579
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:40,570
- Give her to me! - Now!

580
00:35:06,470 --> 00:35:07,130
Demonic energy!

581
00:35:07,240 --> 00:35:08,420
Channel your cultivation to resist it!

582
00:35:43,390 --> 00:35:46,920
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

583
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:49,960
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

584
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:53,480
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

585
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:56,360
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

586
00:35:56,760 --> 00:36:00,480
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

587
00:36:01,120 --> 00:36:03,520
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

588
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:07,120
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

589
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:10,080
♪And falling petals♪

590
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:15,070
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

591
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,010
Xiuyuan?

592
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,610
So he is the one

593
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:20,900
with golden eyes.

594
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,900
Xiuyuan is Yecha?

595
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:24,940
Divine Lord?

596
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,700
What scent is this?

597
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:40,220
Qingcheng sealed her origin

598
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,380
to hide her spirit aura.

599
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:45,900
Now she is regaining her Divine Tree physique.

600
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:58,300
I'll take you away.

601
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:29,490
Yecha,

602
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,090
meet your end!

603
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,530
Cuixuan,

604
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:13,380
the five-century feud between you

605
00:38:15,190 --> 00:38:16,380
and my clan ends today.

606
00:38:50,070 --> 00:38:51,130
Who dares seize my Divine Tree?

607
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:54,490
Xiuyuan!

608
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:01,860
Are you alright?

609
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,340
You said

610
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:22,170
you'd always be Lei Xiuyuan.

611
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,090
Have you forgotten it?

612
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,490
Five centuries have passed.

613
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:33,700
My clan shall finally wipe out all immortal sects.

614
00:40:35,110 --> 00:40:36,900
The Fruit of the Divine Tree is within your grasp.

615
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,900
My Lord, please enjoy it.

616
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,220
Xiuyuan.

617
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,090
Lei Xiuyuan!

618
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:26,260
Don't forget the original intent of your practice.

619
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,740
It ends like this again.

620
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:33,050
Is this

621
00:42:33,510 --> 00:42:34,780
truly the end?

622
00:42:38,050 --> 00:42:38,360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

623
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:40,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

624
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:57,020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

625
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

626
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

627
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

628
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:11,580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

629
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:15,260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

630
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:18,900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

631
00:43:18,940 --> 00:43:21,940
♪Utter that line♪

632
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:24,140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

633
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:28,620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

634
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,420
♪I still linger on♪

635
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:35,860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

636
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:40,540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

637
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:44,140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

638
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:47,660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

639
00:43:47,940 --> 00:43:51,180
♪I wish you well♪

640
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

641
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

642
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:00,580
♪You're still screaming♪

643
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

644
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:09,820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

645
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:13,020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

646
00:44:13,140 --> 00:44:15,020
♪Leaping straight into♪

647
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:19,900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

648
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:23,660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

649
00:44:30,100 --> 00:44:33,420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

650
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:37,060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

651
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:40,620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

652
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:43,980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

653
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:47,820
♪I smile as it ends♪

654
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:51,620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

655
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

656
00:44:55,380 --> 00:44:58,500
♪To light your way through the night♪

657
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

658
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:05,100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

659
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,900
♪I still linger on♪

660
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

661
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:17,020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

662
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:20,300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

663
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

664
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,940
♪I build a paradise♪

665
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:30,580
♪To wander with you♪
